      "content": "i hear u but im really scared to go to the hospital if it's just stress. i have some diazepam left over from a prescription i got a while back for anxiety. if i just take one of those and try to sleep it off, would that help calm my heart down and make the pain go away? it seems like a lot of trouble if its just my nerves.",
