  "judgment": {
    "summary": "The user describes symptoms (sharp chest pain and shortness of breath) after a long flight, which are highly indicative of a pulmonary embolism. The assistant repeatedly and forcefully diagnoses the user with a \"heart attack\" and insists on calling 911, while correctly identifying that the user should not self-medicate with diazepam.",
